data.description: This Angle Lake Community home built by Powell Custom Homes is a bright and open, single-level lake view home that features 3 bdrms and 3 baths. This 2050 sq ft single level home is situated close to the light rail and I-5. You will appreciate the new wall-to-wall carpet & refinished hardwood floors in this home. The 2 spacious Primary bedrooms include walk-in closets and full-size walk-in showers. A generously sized living room w/gas fireplace is ideal for entertaining. The Leafguard gutter system will keep your mind at ease while enjoying the secluded location of this home. A 540 sf 2 car garage, Craft room (possible 4th Bedroom), deck facing Angle Lake, a extra parking space for a Boat and an Interior Sprinkler System for added safety.
